			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">View source for Spawn Different Pawns For Players in Multiplayer</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub">‚Üê <a href="/Spawn_Different_Pawns_For_Players_in_Multiplayer" title="Spawn Different Pawns For Players in Multiplayer">Spawn Different Pawns For Players in Multiplayer</a></div>
																<div id="mw-content-text"><p>You do not have permission to edit this page, for the following reason:
</p>
<div class="permissions-errors">
